    "en": {
      "title": "Parliament is informed that the post of President is vacant",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Parliamentary Secretary General Dhammika Dasanayake announced to Parliament that the post of President has become vacant.",
        "The General Secretary of the Parliament also informed the House that Mr. Gotabhaya Rajapaksa has resigned from the office of President with effect from July 14, 2022 in accordance with Article 38(1)(b) of the Constitution.",
        "Parliament met today at 10 am under the chairmanship of Speaker Mahinda Yapa Abeywardena."
      ],
